me an Internet folk hero in January, thanks to his prescient bets on GameSt=
op stock. For months leading up to the GameStop trading frenzy in January=
=E2=80=94during which nonprofessional traders sent the company=E2=80=99s sh=
ares soaring to a record high=E2=80=94Mr. Gill posted videos and messages d=
iscussing why he was putting large sums of money into the stock. =E2=80=A6<=
/p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">At the time, Mr. Gill was registered as a b=
