y the company and its client-facing registered agents. ...</p><p style=3D"m=
argin: 16px 0;">The office of William Galvin, the Secretary of the Commonwe=
alth of Massachusetts, opened an inquiry into the matter earlier this year.=
 His office said that while MML prohibited broker-dealer employees from dis=
cussing securities on social media, the company didn=E2=80=99t have =E2=80=
=9Creasonable policies and procedures in place to detect and monitor=E2=80=
=9D such activity. At one point in mid-January, Mr. Galvin=E2=80=99s office=
