t; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-st=
yle: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> what=E2=80=99s all this then</a>:</p>=
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">At first no one could explain why =
business was picking up at Betterment, a robo adviser aimed at newbie inves=
tors. There were about 10,000 signups in one day.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"marg=
in: 16px 0;">Then came the answer: A 25-year-old TikToker from Tennessee wa=
s posting videos describing how to retire a millionaire by using the platfo=
rm.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">His name is Austin Hankwitz, and he=E2=
=80=99s managed to land one of the hottest new gigs: full-time =E2=80=9Cfin=
fluencer.=E2=80=9D =E2=80=A6</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Once Bettermen=
t saw the traction it was getting through Hankwitz=E2=80=99s posts, it hire=
d him within a month to plug its services via social media.</p><p style=3D"=
margin: 16px 0;">Wealthfront, another robo adviser, has partnered with abou=
