unications officer.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CQuite fr=
ankly, they=E2=80=99re just better at telling our story than we are,=E2=80=
=9D she said.</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I =E2=80=A6=C2=
=A0okay =E2=80=A6=C2=A0so =E2=80=A6=C2=A0some guy on TikTok is like =E2=80=
=9Cyou=E2=80=99ll be a millionaire if you use Betterment=E2=80=9D and Bette=
